### Task Manager API Test Collection
# You can use the "REST Client" VS Code extension to run these directly.
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Test User",
    "email": "test@test.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login User
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Get Projects (Requires Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Create Project (Requires Token & Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "title": "New Test Project",
    "description": "Created via REST client"
}

### 5. Get Tasks (Requires Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
